          <h3>CHOPR-Led Meeting Launches Multicountry Hospital Study</h3>
          <p>A CHOPR-convened meeting of international collaborators at Bellagio, Italy launched the framework for a landmark multicountry study of hospital nurse staffing and patient outcomes — an effort that would eventually span more than 30 countries and reshape global nursing policy debates.</p>
          <span class="tl-tag">Global Research</span>
        </div>
