          <h3>RN4CAST Project Funded by the European Commission</h3>
          <p>The Registered Nurse Forecasting (RN4CAST) study, co-led by CHOPR, was funded by the European Commission's 7th Framework Programme. Spanning nine European countries, it produced definitive evidence on how nurse staffing and education levels affect patient mortality.</p>
          <span class="tl-tag">EU · RN4CAST</span>
